Package: vigiar
Type: Package
Title: Download Data from the VIGIAR Environmental Health Surveillance Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ryan",
           family = "Santos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "santosry@protonmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")),
    person(given = "vigiar",
           family = "team",
           role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides a programmatic interface to download the complete
    dataset from Brazil's VIGIAR (Vigilância em Saúde Ambiental) public
    Power BI dashboard, maintained by the Brazilian Ministry of Health.
    The package handles Power BI anonymous session management, automatic
    decompression of the DSR (Data Shape Response) format including
    dictionary resolution, and returns tidy tibbles ready for analysis.
    Data includes PM2.5 air quality (annual/monthly), days exceeding WHO
    and CONAMA limits, population exposure by concentration category,
    epidemiological health indicators (attributable fractions, mortality,
    hospitalizations), and indoor solid fuel exposure.
